OL,3,CLabour's antisemitism problem is 'a
OL,4,Cmillion miles from where it was'
OL,6,FAntisemitism was discussed in the
OL,7,Flatest of Granada Reports' monthly
OL,8,Fpolitical programme, The Granada Debate
OL,10,FLabour's problem with antisemitism is
OL,11,F"a million miles" from where it was
OL,12,Fbut everybody in politics has a
OL,13,F"responsibility" to ensure it does not
OL,14,Fbecome mainstream, an MP has said.
OL,16,FCharlotte Nichols, who herself is
OL,17,FJewish, says she has experienced the
OL,18,F"staggering rise" in antisemitism
OL,19,Fsince the conflict in Gaza began, and
OL,20,Foften gets threats aimed at her.
