OL,3,CLabour's antisemitism problem is 'a
OL,4,Cmillion miles from where it was'
OL,6,FSpeaking as part of monthly political
OL,7,Fshow , the Labour MP for North said:
OL,8,F"I've experienced it in terms of some
OL,9,Fof the abuse and threats that come
OL,10,Finto my inbox, but also in terms of
OL,11,Ftrying to live my life as a Jewish
OL,12,Fperson in the UK at the moment," she
OL,13,Fsaid.
OL,15,F"At my synagogue at the weekend there
OL,16,Fwere 20 police officers outside and
OL,17,Fmultiple police vans, that was deemed
OL,18,Fnecessary for the protection of the
OL,19,Fcongregation.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/13
