OL,3,CLabour's antisemitism problem is 'a
OL,4,Cmillion miles from where it was'
OL,6,F"It cannot be right in Britain that
OL,7,Fthat is something that is having to be
OL,8,Fput in place.
OL,10,F"I think the really important thing
OL,11,Fthat we need to do is to is to make
OL,12,Fsure there is additional funding going
OL,13,Finto these interfaith initiatives,
OL,14,Fcommunity spaces and so on, that can
OL,15,Fstart to bring these communities
OL,16,Fcloser together rather than allow them
OL,17,Fto be divided by a conflict that is
OL,18,Ftaking place overseas."
