OL,6,FLabour recently after they were
OL,7,Frecorded making anti-Israel comments
OL,8,Fat a party meeting in .
OL,10,FIt removed support from Rochdale by-
OL,11,Felection candidate Azhar Ali after he
OL,12,Ftold the meeting Israel provoked the
OL,13,Fwar in Gaza.
OL,15,FMr Ali has since after he claimed
OL,16,FIsrael allowed Hamas to carry out its
OL,17,F7 October attack to provide grounds to
OL,18,Finvade Gaza.
