OL,3,CLabour's antisemitism problem is 'a
OL,4,Cmillion miles from where it was'
OL,6,FThe developments were then followed by
OL,7,Fthe news another candidate, Graham
OL,8,FJones, who was seeking re-election in
OL,9,FHyndburn, was also recorded allegedly
OL,10,Fmaking comments about Israel.
OL,12,FIt has been described as one of the
OL,13,Fbiggest crises of Sir Keir Starmer's
OL,14,FLeadership, and has reignited a wider
OL,15,Fdebate around whether antisemitism is
OL,16,Fstill an issue within the Labour party.
OL,18,FBut, Ms Nichols said she believed the
OL,19,Fparty was "a million miles on from
OL,20,Fwhere we were just a few years ago".
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G5/13
