OL,3,CLabour's antisemitism problem is 'a
OL,4,Cmillion miles from where it was'
OL,6,F"The EHRC (Equality and Human Rights
OL,7,FCommission) last year, gave us a clean
OL,8,Fbill of health but ultimately there
OL,9,Fwill be issues that pop up from time
OL,10,Fto time unfortunately the key issue is
OL,11,Fhow we deal with them," she said.
OL,13,F"Labour has been very decisive here in
OL,14,Fremoving both of these candidates and
OL,15,FI'm hopeful that in the future should
OL,16,Fan issue like this come out it will be
OL,17,Fdealt with in the same rough and
OL,18,Frobust way because there is no room
OL,19,Ffor antisemitism in Britain.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G6/13
