OL,3,CLabour's antisemitism problem is 'a
OL,4,Cmillion miles from where it was'
OL,6,F"As someone, alongside being an MP, is
OL,7,FJewish I've seen the appalling rise in
OL,8,Fantisemitism that we have seen across
OL,9,Fthe country since the 7 October and
OL,10,FI'm clear that all of us in politics
OL,11,Fhave a responsibility to make sure
OL,12,Fthat isn't something that is part of
OL,13,Fthe mainstream."
OL,15,FNichols was joined by Liberal Democrat
OL,16,Fcandidate for and Saddleworth East,
OL,17,FSam Al-Hamdani.
OL,19,FHe said he believed the problem
OL,20,Freflected society as a whole.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G7/13
