OL,3,CLabour's antisemitism problem is 'a
OL,4,Cmillion miles from where it was'
OL,6,F"So it is going to be an ongoing
OL,7,Fproblem in all parties, what we need
OL,8,Fto do is act decisively.
OL,10,F"I think there is a little bit of an
OL,11,Fissue for the Labour party in that
OL,12,FCharlotte said it was decisive, but
OL,13,Feven if was - and I wasn't party to
OL,14,Fany of the discussions - it didn't
OL,15,Fcome across as decisive, and if you
OL,16,Fdon't put that across to people
OL,17,Fclearly and simply it gives people
OL,18,Fmore of an opportunity to keep going
OL,19,Fwith those wrong attitudes, so next
OL,20,Ftime I think it would need to be done
OL,21,Fbetter."
