OL,6,FMr Al-Hamdani said the message needed
OL,7,Fto be constantly given to all that
OL,8,Fantisemitism was not acceptable.
OL,10,FHe added: "Intervening at every step,
OL,11,Freminding people again and again,
OL,12,Fstepping in every time there is an
OL,13,Fopportunity to make it clear that this
OL,14,Fis wrong, whether it is with an
OL,15,Findividual or with a group.
