OL,3,CLabour's antisemitism problem is 'a
OL,4,Cmillion miles from where it was'
OL,6,F"We (Liberal Democrats) got a message
OL,7,Ffrom our party HQ this morning
OL,8,Freminding people of the definitions,
OL,9,Freminding people there is support out
OL,10,Fthere and it is every party's
OL,11,Fresponsibility to take those steps
OL,12,Fevery single time they can."
OL,14,FAlso on the programme was Conservative
OL,15,FMP for West, Chris Green.
