OL,6,FWhen asked whether he believed the
OL,7,Fgovernment was doing enough to tackle
OL,8,Fantisemitism he said: "The government
OL,9,Fis doing a huge amount to work with
OL,10,Fthe Jewish community and making sure
OL,11,Fthey are protected to the best of our
OL,12,Fability.
OL,14,F"But this is a societal problem, and
OL,15,Fone of the dangers with antisemitism
OL,16,Fthere' a conflict in the middle east
OL,17,Fand that is then use to weaponise
OL,18,Fattacks against Jewish people right
OL,19,Facross the United Kingdom and right
OL,20,Facross the world.
